{"thag7.5:0.1":"Theragatha 7.5 ","thag7.5:0.2":"Sattakanipata ","thag7.5:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag7.5:0.4":"Sarabhangattheragatha ","thag7.5:1.1":"“Sare hatthehi bhanjitva, ","thag7.5:1.2":"katvana kutimacchisam; ","thag7.5:1.3":"Tena me sarabhangoti, ","thag7.5:1.4":"namam sammutiya ahu. ","thag7.5:2.1":"Na mayham kappate ajja, ","thag7.5:2.2":"sare hatthehi bhanjitum; ","thag7.5:2.3":"Sikkhapada no pannatta, ","thag7.5:2.4":"gotamena yasassina. ","thag7.5:3.1":"Sakalam samattam rogam, ","thag7.5:3.2":"Sarabhango naddasam pubbe; ","thag7.5:3.3":"Soyam rogo dittho, ","thag7.5:3.4":"Vacanakarenatidevassa. ","thag7.5:4.1":"Yeneva maggena gato vipassi, ","thag7.5:4.2":"Yeneva maggena sikhi ca vessabhu; ","thag7.5:4.3":"Kakusandhakonagamano ca kassapo, ","thag7.5:4.4":"Tenanjasena agamasi gotamo. ","thag7.5:5.1":"Vitatanha anadana, ","thag7.5:5.2":"satta buddha khayogadha; ","thag7.5:5.3":"Yehayam desito dhammo, ","thag7.5:5.4":"dhammabhutehi tadibhi. ","thag7.5:6.1":"Cattari ariyasaccani, ","thag7.5:6.2":"anukampaya paninam; ","thag7.5:6.3":"Dukkham samudayo maggo, ","thag7.5:6.4":"nirodho dukkhasankhayo. ","thag7.5:7.1":"Yasmim nivattate dukkham, ","thag7.5:7.2":"samsarasmim anantakam; ","thag7.5:7.3":"Bheda imassa kayassa, ","thag7.5:7.4":"jivitassa ca sankhaya; ","thag7.5:7.5":"Anno punabbhavo natthi, ","thag7.5:7.6":"suvimuttomhi sabbadhi”ti. ","thag7.5:7.7":"… Sarabhango thero … ","thag7.5:7.8":"Sattakanipato nitthito. ","thag7.5:8.0":"Tatruddanam ","thag7.5:8.1":"Sundarasamuddo thero, ","thag7.5:8.2":"thero lakundabhaddiyo; ","thag7.5:8.3":"Bhaddo thero ca sopako, ","thag7.5:8.4":"sarabhango mahaisi; ","thag7.5:8.5":"Sattake pancaka thera, ","thag7.5:8.6":"gathayo pancatimsatiti. "}